Logic Flow

Define antenna parameters
Type (dipole/parabolic/array)
Frequency, dimensions
Calculate radiation pattern
Far-field equations
Coordinate transforms
Visualize in 3D
Radiation lobes
Interactive controls

Pseudocode

1. Set parameters: antenna_type, frequency, dimensions
2. Create angular grid: theta, phi
3. For dipole:
   a. Calculate E_field = sin(theta)
4. For parabolic:
   a. Calculate E_field = J1(sin(theta))/sin(theta)
5. For array:
   a. Calculate array_factor
   b. Multiply by element pattern
6. Normalize and plot
7. Add interactive controls
